<td class="answercell">
    <div class="post-text"><p>Bundler "scopes" its install into this folder based on Ruby engine and version.</p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/carlhuda/bundler/blob/3431d6d/lib/bundler/settings.rb#L78" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/carlhuda/bundler/blob/3431d6d/lib/bundler/settings.rb#L78</a>:</p>

<pre><code>"#{path}/#{Bundler.ruby_scope}"
</code></pre>

<p><code>Bundler.ruby_scope</code> is defined at <a href="https://github.com/carlhuda/bundler/blob/3431d6d/lib/bundler.rb#L141-143" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/carlhuda/bundler/blob/3431d6d/lib/bundler.rb#L141-143</a>:</p>

<pre><code>def ruby_scope
  "#{Bundler.rubygems.ruby_engine}/#{Gem::ConfigMap[:ruby_version]}"
end
</code></pre>
</div>
    <table class="fw">
    <tr>
    <td class="vt">









